window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>What if instead of dying in battle, Richard III awakens in the 21st century? <i>This Time</i> examines the medieval monarch as he adapts to modern technology, medicine, and American culture while investigating his past and what Shakespeare had wrought on his character.</p> <p><i>This Time </i>named General Fiction Finalist in the 2010 Next Generation Indie Book Awards.</p>"; 
